body_html: Hi, I followed the instructions and yesterday I was able to play with tensorflow on jupyter, but today I opened docker and typed docker run -it -p 8888:8888 gcr.io/tensorflow/tensorflow and it downloaded again and in docker machine looks like everything is ok, but when I open the browser it says the server needed too much time to answer and im unable to connect. Could someody please suggest a solution?
